    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 50 gp; <b>Weight</b> 8 lbs.</p>\r\n<p>This <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/tools-kits#TOC-Kit-Disguise\">disguise kit</a> includes metallic or stone-colored makeup and cloth that you can apply to appear to be a statue; it grants a +2 bonus only on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/disguise\">Disguise</a> checks to resemble metal, stone, or similar materials. You take a -5 penalty on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/disguise\">Disguise</a> checks when impersonating an inanimate object. A viewer can attempt a single <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\">Perception</a> check opposed by your <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/disguise\">Disguise</a> check upon viewing you, and an additional check each time a creature interacts with you. This kit is <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Exhausted\">exhausted</a> after 10 uses.</p>\r\n\r\n",
